Package io.github.tigerbotics7125.tigerlib.vision

Class SnakeEyes

java.lang.Object
io.github.tigerbotics7125.tigerlib.vision.SnakeEyes
public class SnakeEyes extends Object
This class removes a lot of boiler plate code when designing vison logic, and allows for some comfort features such as caching results.
